> Enjoy all of your favorite snacks, free from the top allergens! This bundle box contains a full assortment of 38 handpicked snacks, including: Popcorners, Herr's chips, Skinny Pop, Capri Sun, Airheads, Partake cookies, Madegood granola bars, Welch's fruit snacks and Fit Joy pretzels.

> Your order will ship separately from your HF meals and may not arrive on your scheduled weekly delivery date. Shipping is included in the total price. Customization of bundles is not available at this time. Contents are subject to change based on availability.

> Click download to view nutrition and allergen information.

Add @Popcorners Kettle Corn Chips{4%unit}, @Herr Foods Inc Good Natured Veg-Ables Snacks{2%unit}, @Skinny Pop 100 Calorie Popcorn{4%unit}, @Capri Sun Juice Pouch Variety Pack{5%unit}, @Airheads Variety{4%unit}, @Partake Crunchy Chocolate Chip{3%unit}, @Made Good Chocolate Chip Granola Mini{4%unit}, @Welch's Mixed Fruit Snacks{6%unit}, and @Fit Joy Pretzels{4%unit} to your allergen friendly box.

Enjoy!